</head>
<div class="over"><div class="Guide">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="card">
      <p class="title"><b><i>THS Gallery - Closure</i></b></p>
      <p class="title">I shut down the gallery, 19/4/2026</p>
      <p class="para">Sorry.</p>
      <p class="para">Hiya! Karis here, Square Enix sent me a DMCA notice for specifically the gallery. It's my first DMCA (let's hope it stays that way), so I just took the subdomain down immediately. I was also notified that <i>Accord's Library</i>, a previous archival site, had their gallery DMCA'd before the main site. That's scary, huh?<br><br> Anyway, nice to meet you.</p>
